➜红旗E-HS9上市、本田S2000将被复活...丨今日车闻
http://www.sohu.com/a/436387639_119212	7384
<p><strong>电动车也能有这么强的气场，红旗E-HS9上市</strong></p>
<p>12月4日晚，红旗宣布E-HS9上市，它带来了4款车型，官方指导价定在了50.98-72.98万元。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201205/8853116423fc47a8a65ff8422ad0822b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201205/5c1b8e3abcb642e6baf652498651ef6a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201205/7c2aba4f75394bd6ae4d7c460e2e2522.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
